<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"/></head><body><table style="border-collapse:collapse;width:100%;"><tr><th style="background-color:#FFFF00;font-weight:bold;border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;padding:4px;">Hospid</th><th style="background-color:#FFFF00;font-weight:bold;border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;padding:4px;">Hospname</th><th style="background-color:#FFFF00;font-weight:bold;border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;padding:4px;">City</th><th style="background-color:#FFFF00;font-weight:bold;border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;padding:4px;">Terms</th><th style="background-color:#FFFF00;font-weight:bold;border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;padding:4px;">Conditions</th><th style="background-color:#FFFF00;font-weight:bold;border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;padding:4px;">Note</th></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">44890</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">United Superspeciality Hospital And Trauma Center (Cnb Medicon Llp)</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">GONDIA</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Doctor's fee, OT charges, Anasthetic Charges, Drugs, Investigations, Professional charges, Room rents, Nursing &amp; administrative charges. All other charges not mentioned in L2,L3 &amp; L4</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">44890</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">United Superspeciality Hospital And Trauma Center (Cnb Medicon Llp)</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">GONDIA</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">IOL,Pacemaker, Ortho prosthesis, Stents, staplers</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">44890</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">United Superspeciality Hospital And Trauma Center (Cnb Medicon Llp)</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">GONDIA</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Assays, high end hormonal studies, SPECT, A scans,etc.</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">44890</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">United Superspeciality Hospital And Trauma Center (Cnb Medicon Llp)</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">GONDIA</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Laproscopy/abdominal/vaginal/laser etc</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">44890</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">United Superspeciality Hospital And Trauma Center (Cnb Medicon Llp)</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">GONDIA</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">All General Surgeries with or wothout adhenolysis are within same package. For Hernia, laproscopic surgeries 15% extra than hernia open surgeries can be given.</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">44890</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">United Superspeciality Hospital And Trauma Center (Cnb Medicon Llp)</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">GONDIA</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">For C3R, Insurance Companies will not pay for Intacs lens which is for vision correction.</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">44890</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">United Superspeciality Hospital And Trauma Center (Cnb Medicon Llp)</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">GONDIA</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Ready to provide 10% discount on Hospital SOC including medicine and consumables.(Except NPPA capped items,DPCO Drugs). Except agreed packages and agreed tariff for all cashless and Reimbursement cases</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">44890</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">United Superspeciality Hospital And Trauma Center (Cnb Medicon Llp)</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">GONDIA</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Packages are walk in walkout packages for patients unless specified otherwise for the procedures where implants are to be charged extra.</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">44890</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">United Superspeciality Hospital And Trauma Center (Cnb Medicon Llp)</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">GONDIA</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">The packages includes room stay,routine tests, routine diagnostics, OT charges, Surgeons fees, Anaesthesia, Dr's visit fees (admitting Doctor) and medicines/consumables (list of Investigations included) &amp; NME</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">44890</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">United Superspeciality Hospital And Trauma Center (Cnb Medicon Llp)</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">GONDIA</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">In cases of multiple surgeries major surgery will be approved 100%, 2nd surgery @ 50% of package and 3rd surgery @ 25% of agreed package.</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">44890</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">United Superspeciality Hospital And Trauma Center (Cnb Medicon Llp)</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">GONDIA</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Blood/Blood products will be charged as per actuals. Additional stay, medicines and consumables outside the limits will be charged as per actuals after giving due justification to the TPA</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">44890</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">United Superspeciality Hospital And Trauma Center (Cnb Medicon Llp)</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">GONDIA</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Investigations does not include high end tests such as CT, MRI, 2D Echo, Stress Test,,SMA+12 etc. which will be charged on actuals as per tariff. (List of investigations are included ENCL)</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">44890</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">United Superspeciality Hospital And Trauma Center (Cnb Medicon Llp)</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">GONDIA</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Pre-Operative investigation are included in package amount. Investigation included in packages- CBC, Urine Routine, HIV Spot, Anti HCV, HbsAG, Serum Creatinine, LFT,RFT,USG,X-ray and ECG.</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">44890</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">United Superspeciality Hospital And Trauma Center (Cnb Medicon Llp)</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">GONDIA</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Emergency charges will be applicable only for cases hospitalized on Public Holidays &amp; Sundays and from 10PM to 7AM on weekdays.</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">44890</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">United Superspeciality Hospital And Trauma Center (Cnb Medicon Llp)</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">GONDIA</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">During Emergency time, 15% extra will be considered for above mention packages.</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">44890</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">United Superspeciality Hospital And Trauma Center (Cnb Medicon Llp)</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">GONDIA</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Agreed Rates will be applicable for 2 years from the Approval date.</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">44890</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">United Superspeciality Hospital And Trauma Center (Cnb Medicon Llp)</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">GONDIA</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Packages applicable for ICU admission &amp; ICU discharge will be as per room eligiblity of patient max upto private room</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">44890</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">United Superspeciality Hospital And Trauma Center (Cnb Medicon Llp)</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">GONDIA</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">One Surgery is as per GIPSA and other Non GIPSA, then the higher category surgery will be charged 100% and subsquent surgery will be charged 50%</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">44890</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">United Superspeciality Hospital And Trauma Center (Cnb Medicon Llp)</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">GONDIA</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">If Hospital rack rates found to be lower than offered rates, than lower rates will be applied for claim settlement for cardholders.</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">44890</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">United Superspeciality Hospital And Trauma Center (Cnb Medicon Llp)</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">GONDIA</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">No Services charge/ Surcharge will be applicable for cardholders.</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">44890</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">United Superspeciality Hospital And Trauma Center (Cnb Medicon Llp)</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">GONDIA</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">If the insured opts for a room rent higher than the eligibility as per the Sum Insured under the policy, proportionate deductions will be applicable on the entire package wherever applicable.</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">44890</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-w