000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Hospital will submit the revised proposal along with the revised hospital SOC 3 months prior to the due date for renewal.</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">49322</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Aadhya Multispeciality Hospital</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Gondia</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Hernia packages are inclusive of mesh upto Rs. 7000/-. Tracker are excluded.</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">49322</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Aadhya Multispeciality Hospital</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Gondia</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Cost of lenses for imported foldable IOL will be payable max upto Rs. 7000/-. For lower lenses like hard lens cost will be at actuals.Maximum admisability for IOL cost will be Rs. 7000/-. The rate shall be subject to changes as per the Govt./NPPA guidelines issued from time to time.</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">49322</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Aadhya Multispeciality Hospital</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Gondia</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Hospital endevour for GENINS INDIA declaration form for all claims of GENINS INDIA cardholders. In case patient declines to sign declaration form, the hospital will endorse said remark on the declaration form and inform the TPA/Insurance company accordingly. The hospital will desplay the notice of declaration form at prominent place in their hospital as per our website to educate the patient for better service.</td></tr><tr><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">49322</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Aadhya Multispeciality Hospital</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Gondia</td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;"></td><td style="border:1px solid #000;white-space:normal;word-break:break-word;word-wrap:break-word;padding:4px;">Complience to IRDA circular IRDAI/HLT/GDUCIRI 1 1 4107 12018 is mandatory.</td></tr><t